  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "When you have a repo URL with a path (e.g. `http://example.com/helm`) along with a chart URL (defined in `index.yaml`) which is relative (e.g. `charts/foo-1.2.3.tgz`), the resulting download URL is wrong: `http://example.com/helmchart/foo-1.2.3.tgz`. \r\n\r\nThis is due to the path concatenation logic in the `ResolveChartVersion` function, which has been altered by this commit:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kubernetes/helm/pull/2988/files\r\n",
